long_description: for over 50 years we've taken care of families, businesses, non-profits and other community members. don-rick has grown into a leading independent insurance agency with four locations across wisconsin. don-rick insurance was formed in 1971 when don olson of portage, wi and rick lewison of baraboo, wi merged their agencies. they established the groundwork for a successful business model; expecting accountability, teamwork and initiative, that helped get the agency where it is today. in 1993, rick's eldest son, eric lewison started in the portage office as a commercial insurance agent. in 1994, rick's youngest son, dan lewison started in the baraboo office as a personal lines agent. mitch is a fourth-generation independent insurance agent with deep expertise in the business and personal insurance space. our mission statement says it all: "we are committed to being the best for our customers, communities and companies.". don-rick insurance is a full-service insurance agency providing insurance for individuals and businesses.
